Privacy Policy for TechRoute.pk

Last Updated: October 29, 2023

1. Introduction

Welcome to TechRoute.pk, a free app developed by KhudiTechnology. Your privacy and the security of your personal information are important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our service.

2. Information Collection and Use

By using TechRoute.pk, you agree to the collection and use of your personal information as described in this policy. The information we collect is used for providing and enhancing our Service. We do not use or share your information except as outlined in this Privacy Policy.

3. Information You Provide

When you add an event, community, or course, we collect your profile picture from your Google account, your name, and email address. This information is essential for other users to identify the creator of the event, community, or course and to facilitate communication and interaction among users.

4. How We Use Your Information

We use the collected information to:

Enable users to identify the creators of events, communities, and courses.
Facilitate communication between users who join or register for events, communities, or courses.
Enhance and personalize your experience with our app.
5. Data Storage

We store all user data, including event, community, and course information, in Firebase Realtime Database and Firestore. These platforms, provided by Google, adhere to strict data security standards, ensuring the confidentiality and integrity of your information. Your data is encrypted and protected; however, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is entirely secure.

6. Log Data and Cookies

In case of app errors, we collect Log Data, including your device's IP address, device name, operating system version, app configuration, usage time, and other statistics. While the app itself does not use cookies, third-party services we employ might use them for data collection and service improvement. You can choose to accept or refuse these cookies.

7. Service Providers

We may employ third-party companies and individuals to provide and analyze our Service. These third parties have access to your Personal Information solely to perform tasks on our behalf and are obligated not to disclose or use it for any other purpose.

8. Security

We use commercially acceptable means to protect your Personal Information. However, no internet transmission or electronic storage method is 100% secure. While we strive to use reliable methods, we cannot guarantee absolute security.

9. Links to Other Sites

Our Service may contain links to external sites not operated by us. We strongly recommend reviewing the Privacy Policy of these websites, as we have no control over their content, privacy policies, or practices.

10. Links to Third-Party Privacy Policies

TechRoute.pk uses several third-party services to enhance your experience. Below are the links to the privacy policies of these service providers:

Google Play Services: Google Play Services is used to update Google apps and apps from Google Play. You can review Google's privacy policy using the provided link.

AdMob: AdMob is Google's advertising platform. You can learn more about AdMob's privacy practices by visiting the linked privacy policy.

Google Analytics for Firebase: Google Analytics for Firebase is an analytics service provided by Google. For details on how Google Analytics for Firebase handles your data, please refer to the privacy policy provided.

Firebase Crashlytics: Firebase Crashlytics is a crash reporting service provided by Google. You can find information about how Crashlytics handles your data in the linked privacy policy.

11. Childrenâ€™s Privacy

TechRoute.pk does not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and discover that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us, and we will promptly delete it.

12. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy, and any changes will be reflected on this page. We advise you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any updates.

13. Contact Us

If you have questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at khuditechnology@gmail.com.
